WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.326 --> 00:00:01.063
Good morning, family!

00:00:01.309 --> 00:00:18.453
Praise the Lord, I have some exciting news to tell you all.

00:00:18.453 --> 00:00:25.657
We started our French channel yesterday, we started our Arabic channel, and we've started our Portuguese channel.

00:00:25.657 --> 00:00:56.200
So if you speak those languages, these are exciting times for you, I guess, if you like watching me.

00:00:56.200 --> 00:01:02.320
We're working hard, folks.

00:01:02.320 --> 00:01:47.880
My son and my wife, we're all downloading and getting this channel set up, spreading the gospel throughout the whole world.

00:01:47.880 --> 00:02:05.300
Now I will go to what I've seen about Israel.

00:02:22.307 --> 00:02:22.833
I was interceding for Israel and what's about to happen.

00:02:29.246 --> 00:02:53.720
The moment Trump is inaugurated on the 20th, I saw him come out like a lion cracking his whip.

00:03:10.528 --> 00:03:24.528
I'm talking big, but you know how they say some dogs are all bark and no bite?

00:03:24.528 --> 00:03:49.420
No, he is all dog and all bite from what I've seen coming.

00:03:59.639 --> 00:04:00.299
I saw things that were strategic.

00:04:00.299 --> 00:04:39.056
He has a plan, and I saw strategic plans for taking out key, select targets in the Middle East—I'm talking within a small span of time.

00:04:39.056 --> 00:04:51.969
I'm talking about using the military like a chess game.

00:05:01.199 --> 00:05:01.909
I saw Iran crippled financially.

00:05:01.909 --> 00:05:23.427
A great disruption, a great delay, and a great setback is coming to Iran.

00:05:23.427 --> 00:06:00.119
Remember what I just said: a great disruption, a great delay, and a great setback is coming to Iran financially, with their nuclear capabilities and any kind of technology.

00:06:17.250 --> 00:06:17.720
A great setback is coming to Iran.

00:06:24.646 --> 00:06:41.208
With Hamas and all this stuff, we're talking about the big dogs coming on the stage.

00:06:41.208 --> 00:07:14.999
I saw weapons—this is interesting, I want you to think about this—I saw weapons that the United States has never used in battle before.

00:07:14.999 --> 00:07:32.870
They are going to use weapons that our country has never used in battle.

00:07:32.870 --> 00:07:55.188
Maybe we've practiced with them, but we've never used them in battle on any foreign adversary.

00:07:55.188 --> 00:08:24.079
I saw a hypersonic missile—this right here—this is the missile that I saw them using strategically in Iran and on Hezbollah targets.

00:08:24.079 --> 00:08:52.690
I saw them coming out of ships in the Mediterranean and a heavy military presence with our aircraft carriers and our battleships.

00:08:52.690 --> 00:09:31.022
I'm talking a heavy presence in the Mediterranean, the Red Sea, and around the oceans there as an intimidation like you've never seen before in that strait where they're always picking on those ships.

00:09:31.022 --> 00:09:52.262
I'm talking a heavy military presence and the respect that America has lost with our foreign adversaries over the last four years.

00:09:52.262 --> 00:10:14.680
We have been the laughingstock of the world, and when he comes in, I saw respect restored back to America like you wouldn't believe.

00:10:31.097 --> 00:10:38.190
I saw in the spirit a type and shadow of a Ronald Reagan coming back into power, but even stronger.

00:10:38.190 --> 00:11:01.200
Respect is coming back to America; people are going to take America seriously again for this window.

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:59.176
We are going to have to pray for the next four years because a major bulldog is coming on the scene, and you will see him even more aggressive than he was four years ago.

00:12:05.320 --> 00:12:09.790
It would be eight years ago now.

00:12:09.790 --> 00:12:19.104
Wow, isn't it amazing how fast time goes?

00:12:22.360 --> 00:12:29.866
I saw him hitting strategic targets in Iran and in Syria.

00:12:29.866 --> 00:12:44.310
It's going to look like shock and awe for what I have seen coming, folks.

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:57.554
It was like, 'You all have messed with the wrong folks.

00:12:57.554 --> 00:13:33.473
' This has been going on too long, the bullying and all this stuff, and I'm telling you, I saw a cracking of a whip over the Middle East.

00:13:40.665 --> 00:13:48.743
I saw strategic alliances and people saying, 'We're back in business.

00:13:48.743 --> 00:14:18.400
' You've got the 'open' sign in your window and everybody's excited, saying, 'Come on in and buy the goods again.

00:14:18.400 --> 00:14:27.627
' I'm talking 'drill, baby, drill.

00:14:27.627 --> 00:14:54.320
' You're going to see oil like you've never seen it in a long time.

00:14:54.320 --> 00:15:05.800
You're going to see pipelines getting established and major stuff starting to happen again.

00:15:05.800 --> 00:15:09.920
Jobs, jobs, jobs.

00:15:09.920 --> 00:15:13.731
Putting America first.

00:15:13.731 --> 00:15:28.240
You're going to see patriotism come back to the people.

00:15:28.240 --> 00:15:36.299
Our foreign adversaries will be scared.

00:15:37.080 --> 00:15:43.120
The Lord showed me this: Do you remember when I told you there was going to be a time of great seedtime and harvest?

00:15:43.120 --> 00:16:05.302
An acceleration of seedtime and harvest—it did not have to do just with finances.

00:16:05.302 --> 00:16:22.293
Everything that we have sowed in the past would come to harvest at last.

00:16:25.420 --> 00:16:44.613
If you had bad seeds in the ground, you needed to repent and call crop failure over those seeds.

00:16:44.613 --> 00:17:21.959
Say, 'Father, I've sowed some bad seeds, and I repent and I take communion over those seeds,' and ask God for mercy.

00:17:21.959 --> 00:18:17.040
I saw a dividing line when it comes to the church—the ones that are truly for him and the ones that are riding the fence.

00:18:17.040 --> 00:18:28.075
Judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:18:30.299 --> 00:18:44.270
I told you there would be a cleaning of the house—sexual sins and corruption.

00:18:54.960 --> 00:18:56.960
The Lord showed me the church being scrubbed down and cleaned up.

00:18:56.960 --> 00:19:21.665
When the cleaning of this happens at a greater level in 2025—we've seen the beginning in 2024—it's going to accelerate even more this year.

00:19:21.665 --> 00:19:38.406
You're going to see more ministries being called out.

00:19:38.406 --> 00:20:14.474
It's not just going to be seeker-friendly charismatics; it's going to be all denominations: Catholic, Methodist, Baptist, and the Church of Christ.

00:20:15.571 --> 00:20:28.330
A cleaning of the house is coming to the body of Christ.

00:20:28.330 --> 00:20:51.560
God said to me, 'Brandon, I told you I was bringing forth the new Davids.

00:20:51.560 --> 00:21:43.053
' You will see a new generation that is not in the big spotlight on the TVs with all the money and the jets; they are the guys who have been the janitors, raised up for such a time as this.

00:21:47.310 --> 00:22:01.341
In 2025, you will see new faces that seem to come out of nowhere.

00:22:01.341 --> 00:22:39.690
You're going to see people walk in an anointing you've never seen before, while others who walked in it won't walk in it anymore.

00:22:39.690 --> 00:22:50.224
It'll be like the light switch turned off.

00:22:50.224 --> 00:23:18.867
All of a sudden, the lights are going to start going out on those people, and they'll fade into the background.

00:23:18.867 --> 00:23:36.400
God said, 'I'm raising up a new people; behold, I do a new thing.

00:23:36.400 --> 00:23:53.735
' He said it's a form of punishment—a 'time-out' for some folks.

00:23:53.735 --> 00:24:03.485
I warned you about the ten cities.

00:24:04.940 --> 00:24:25.520
The Lord said, 'Brandon, I want you to notice what color they were—blue or red?

00:24:25.520 --> 00:24:35.223
' He said it's far-left thinking versus conservative values.

00:24:35.223 --> 00:25:00.629
Out of all the ten cities he alerted me to pray for, every single one of them was deep blue.

00:25:00.629 --> 00:25:18.1000
It's not the Lord punishing them; it's seedtime and harvest.

00:25:18.1000 --> 00:25:59.599
When you are in a deep blue area like Los Angeles—I've interceded for the fires, but it's like pushing against a wall.

00:25:59.599 --> 00:26:44.039
Sometimes you'll be praying for a city and you'll feel there is a wall there that you're just not able to get over in the spirit realm.

00:26:44.299 --> 00:26:53.620
I felt like I was pushing against mud over these fires.

00:26:59.593 --> 00:27:43.120
The Lord showed me: 'If my people, who are called by my name, will humble themselves and turn from their wicked ways, then I will hear from heaven and I will heal their land.

00:27:43.120 --> 00:28:57.559
' But if you have a group of people in a deep blue area that are continually in the school systems teaching kids corrupt things—all the liberal trash they're feeding and pushing—it causes the umbrella of prayer covering to be lifted.

00:28:57.559 --> 00:29:13.990
In red areas, there is a lot of intercessory prayer covering.

00:29:13.990 --> 00:29:57.210
But in a big blue area full of radical thinking, pornography, pedophilia rings, and witchcraft in Hollywood, the door is opened and the enemy comes in like a snake.

00:29:57.210 --> 00:30:41.871
When you take your hand and say, 'I don't want God in this area; I don't want the Ten Commandments,' God stands back and says, 'If you don't want anything to do with me, then have your way.

00:30:41.871 --> 00:30:52.600
' It's like Lot in the middle of Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:30:52.600 --> 00:31:13.355
Abraham was on the hill praying for Lot, and God had to send angels to get him out.

00:31:13.891 --> 00:31:23.151
Is God telling you to leave a blue area?

00:31:23.151 --> 00:32:01.000
If you are living in Portland, Seattle, San Francisco, LA, Las Vegas, Dallas, New Orleans, Nashville, Boston, Chicago, New York, or Miami, you should pray very hard.

00:32:08.585 --> 00:32:09.640
Lot was spared because he left the area.

00:32:09.640 --> 00:32:15.669
The cup of sin was full.

00:32:15.669 --> 00:32:31.729
In this last 2024 election, he told me he was watching to see how they vote.

00:32:42.799 --> 00:33:13.171
You can keep going down a road in rebellion for so long, passing dead-end signs and stoplights, but you chose to vote Gavin Newsom in; you chose this direction with Nancy Pelosi.

00:33:13.171 --> 00:33:18.000
By a majority, you took the hand of prayer off of you.

00:33:18.000 --> 00:33:30.679
When you try to pray against it, it's like hitting a wall.

00:33:30.679 --> 00:34:03.102
If you live in a very dark area, you better pray if you're supposed to be there, because it might cost you your life.

00:34:03.102 --> 00:34:07.960
Follow the voice of God.

00:34:07.960 --> 00:34:34.818
If you feel God stationed you there, then be there and plead the blood over your family.

00:34:34.818 --> 00:34:59.700
Over this whole year of 2025, you will see a dividing line of blessing and favor when it comes to droughts, storms, and earthquakes.

00:34:59.700 --> 00:35:10.108
You've opened the door for attack.

00:35:25.730 --> 00:35:25.980
How did they vote?

00:35:25.980 --> 00:35:33.658
They voted for abortion rights and against the unborn.

00:35:33.658 --> 00:35:49.359
This is a big no-no to the Lord, shedding innocent blood.

00:35:54.226 --> 00:36:02.462
You will see great favor and blessing on red states.

00:36:03.575 --> 00:36:21.365
I saw them rising up with torches, and I saw fire come on the central part of America.

00:36:21.365 --> 00:36:43.471
I saw a mass migration of Americans leaving the East Coast and New York because of what's coming.

00:36:43.471 --> 00:36:57.960
We have a window of opportunity to get prepared.

00:36:57.960 --> 00:37:05.067
This is funding for the harvest.

00:37:25.720 --> 00:37:27.114
The money will come to the remnant to supply food, water, and buildings.

00:37:27.114 --> 00:37:46.297
The Lord said it is a small window, and then you will see the house of cards fall.

00:37:46.297 --> 00:37:54.559
I know it's in the winter months.

00:38:06.840 --> 00:38:07.040
The blue states will look like Ichabod.

00:38:07.040 --> 00:38:36.839
Remember my words: The cities will look like an Ichabod, but it is not an Ichabod; it is a shaking to awaken.

00:38:36.839 --> 00:38:48.220
True judgment is separation from God for eternity.

00:38:48.220 --> 00:39:18.900
It's time for the church to preach the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ and stop preaching the lukewarm gospel.

00:39:18.900 --> 00:39:28.280
Seeker-friendly stuff is going to go away.

00:39:28.280 --> 00:39:44.980
In dominant red areas, I saw a mighty move of the spirit.

00:39:44.980 --> 00:40:07.400
I saw a mass migration of Americans coming for the revival that kicks off in Oklahoma.

00:40:14.023 --> 00:40:22.731
You won't even be able to find a house to buy there.

00:40:22.731 --> 00:40:57.057
It will be like light and dark; you will see gross darkness in some places, but where it's light, you will see the fire of God.

00:40:57.057 --> 00:41:14.720
I told you great darkness was coming to the East Coast.

00:41:14.720 --> 00:41:28.730
If you're called there, be a light in that darkness.

00:41:28.730 --> 00:41:40.986
My job is to tell you a massive storm is coming.

00:41:40.986 --> 00:42:04.040
The light will get lighter, and the dark will get darker, like labor pains.

00:42:04.040 --> 00:42:15.180
I'm not a prophet; I'm a Watchman.

00:42:21.800 --> 00:42:23.143
My job is to warn you.

00:42:23.143 --> 00:42:35.040
God's not out of mercy; he's out of time.

00:42:40.839 --> 00:42:57.434
You invite demons in when you put a satanic statue next to the Ten Commandments.

00:43:00.970 --> 00:43:11.825
The devil's whole mission is to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:43:11.825 --> 00:43:31.800
From San Diego all the way up the coastline, there is an open door over your cities.

00:43:31.800 --> 00:43:44.560
Look at the news; your cities are burning up right now.

00:43:47.604 --> 00:44:09.480
It will be more intense in the days ahead, and people will say it is a great Ichabod.

00:44:09.480 --> 00:44:17.719
But God never leaves his people.

00:44:17.719 --> 00:44:33.344
If you humble yourself and pray, he will heal the land.

00:44:43.700 --> 00:44:44.065
You opened the door with your vote.

00:44:44.065 --> 00:45:12.233
Gavin Newsom is thinking with a reprobate mind, but you see Trump operating with wisdom because he blesses Israel.

00:45:17.710 --> 00:45:27.393
You will see this come to light even more from 2025 to 2028.

00:45:27.393 --> 00:45:36.114
Enter through the narrow gate.

00:45:36.114 --> 00:45:43.573
Who will you serve this day?

00:45:43.573 --> 00:45:49.064
Run to the light.

00:45:49.064 --> 00:45:56.920
This is the last call.

00:45:56.920 --> 00:46:10.592
The next four years will increase in shaking every single year.

00:46:10.592 --> 00:46:32.400
The church will rise up, and when people see how blessed we are, they will run to the light.

00:46:36.520 --> 00:46:54.107
They will see that there is no Ichabod with you; we see no Ichabod.

00:46:54.107 --> 00:47:06.212
Get ready for the best days you've ever had.

00:47:20.485 --> 00:47:20.730
We will see the greatest harvest of souls.

00:47:20.730 --> 00:47:35.189
I call the unsaved loved ones born again in Jesus' name.

00:47:40.525 --> 00:47:45.593
I thank God for divine protection over President Trump.

00:47:53.665 --> 00:47:59.960
I cover this house, our finances, and our children in the blood of Jesus.

00:48:05.160 --> 00:48:11.693
A thousand shall fall at our side, but it will not come near us.

00:48:13.048 --> 00:48:32.719
We call down terrorist attacks and ask for the authorities to expose the darkness and put those responsible in Guantanamo Bay.

00:48:47.884 --> 00:48:48.119
Our redemption is drawing nigh.

00:48:54.564 --> 00:48:56.400
We call for healing and strong marriages.

00:48:57.893 --> 00:49:02.874
On fire brush arbor churches are coming.

00:49:02.874 --> 00:49:04.799
Put a smile on your face because Jesus loves you.

00:49:04.799 --> 00:49:06.500
God bless you all.
